data.description: Welcome to Home Sweet Home in the small town of Hilliard. This 3 bed 2 bath home sits on a cul-de-sac with no HOA or CDD. This home boasts stunning curb appeal, a new metal roof, a shed for storage, and fresh Shark coating on the garage and back patio floors. Inside, there is kitchen, living, and dining with a pantry and laundry. The split floor plan offers privacy for the Owners Suite, which features an en-suite with a spacious vanity with a seating area, an oversized bathtub, walk in closet, and private water closet with a walk-in shower. Two bedrooms and a full hall bath complete this wonderful home. New fencing has been added around the backyard with walk in and drive in entry. Come and see!
